Mobile & Online
An easy and secure way to access your bank accounts









Personal
                                >
                                Banking
                                >
                                Mobile and Online
                            








                            Bank wherever you are
                        

Want to get balance alerts, transfer money and pay bills online or from your mobile device? Or deposit checks from your smartphone? 
Bell's mobile and online banking lets you take your bank with you – and it's free, secure and easy.




            I am always impressed with the customer service at Bell Bank. I feel they truly care about me and I am not just another number.
        
-Becky B.
        



                                    Personal Online Banking
                                
With Bell's Personal Online Banking you can bank anytime, anywhere!

Check account balances for checking, savings, CDs and loans with Bell    
View real-time account balances, check images and history
Transfer funds between your accounts, including those at other banks 
Pay bills online
Pay other people electronically with Popmoney 
Sign up for email or text alerts about your accounts
Export history to financial software or spreadsheets
Get online statements to cut down on paper


                                    Mobile Banking
                                
Use your smartphone or other mobile devices to take your bank wherever you are.

Mobile Banking App – Just download our free Bell Bank smartphone app from your iPhone®, iPad® or Android™ app store, log in using your Personal Online Banking login and password, and you’ve got online banking including transfers, standard bill pay, Popmoney person-to-person payments and ATM/location finder.
Mobile Check Deposit – Use the Bell Bank mobile app’s free Mobile Check Deposit feature to take a picture of your check with your mobile device, then submit the image to our bank for deposit to your account.
Mobile Wallet – Simplify your everyday purchases by adding your Bell debit card to your mobile wallet. If your smartphone has Android PayTM, Apple PayTM or Samsung PayTM, you can pay with a tap or a touch of your finger.
Mobile Text Banking – Text your bank, and it texts you back! With free Mobile Text Banking, you can use texting on your mobile phone to access account balances, transfer funds, and receive alerts about deposits and withdrawals. (Message and data rates may apply. See bellbanks.com for full terms and conditions. Text STOP to 226563 to cancel.) 

Just download the Bell Bank app from your app store to get started. 



                                    Online & Mobile Bill Pay
                                
Pay your bills with the press of a button!
Bill Pay lets you schedule ongoing payments for regular bills such as car loans, mortgage payments, cable, utilities or insurance premiums. At Bell Bank, standard Bill Pay with unlimited transactions comes free with your personal checking account; there may be a fee for expedited Bill Pay. 
Log in to Personal Online Banking to sign up for online Bill Pay.





            Why Bell
        



You’re busy and you need a bank that’s with you wherever you go. At Bell, we understand the importance of convenience, and we deliver.








