Bell Bank is a strong, growing, forward-looking organization with world-class employees. At Bell Bank, we have a very unusual “bottom line.” While most companies focus on efficiency and finances, Bell Bank has been different from the start. Our bottom line is simple: “Happy Employees! Happy Customers!” Our focus truly is on our greatest resource, our employees.
Current Job Openings
We have the following job opportunities available: 




Loan Officer Assistant: Phoenix, A.Z.
Processing Supervisor: Minneapolis, Minn.

