Process small pipeline of Home Mortgage loans as needed
Maintain up to date knowledge of all agency/investor/federal guidelines as well as Bell policies and procedures
Directly resolve or coordinate resolution of client related issues
Resolve “on hold” and “pend” issues as needed to ensure timely purchase of loan files
Report to senior management any issues with polices/procedures and make recommendations for change to improve efficiencies
Work with other Department supervisors to ensure/maintain effective communication and resolve issues.
Ability to coach, mentor and raise level of talent throughout the branch
Support Bell strategic growth and recruiting efforts as directed
Perform other duties as assigned by Sr. Management

