3-5 years Mortgage Operations experience
Thorough understanding of all agency/investor/federal mortgage banking guidelines
Ability to effectively manage and monitor the performance of others and provide effective feedback
Excellent verbal and written communication skills
Ability to manage many diverse tasks and deadlines as well as willingness to set and ensure deadlines for others

Bell Bank Mortgage provides competitive compensation and an excellent benefits package.
