Job Summary:
This position is responsible for supporting Loan Origination System users by managing help desk tickets. As tickets are submitted this role would own the resolution of the request, until it can be solved or handed off to another team member. The Encompass User Support Specialist will acknowledge the issue, figure out a priority.  It is expected that this position will respond with an acknowledge response to incoming help requests within minutes of the submission between the hours of 8 am and 5 pm.  The Encompass Help Desk will know and understand basic Encompass functionality as well as learn the Bell workflow.
Primary Duties:

