ShareOverview & States ServedBell State Bank & Trust is a branch bank founded in 1966 and headquartered in Fargo, ND. It operates 21 branches in 3 states.Based on its fees, size, and account interest rates this bank receives a Smart Rating of 93 out of 100, which is better than the average of 88 for a regional bank.Click the button below to view a list of banks sorted by Smart Rating.Top 10 Banks  with highest Smart Rating  >> 





