ShareCertificates of Deposit

Current CD Yields



Offer DetailsBell State Bank & Trust offers a 6-month certificate of deposit (CD) with an APY of 0.15%, which is a bit worse than the APY offered by other banks on 60-month CDs. For those interested in a longer term CD, Bell State Bank & Trust offers a 60-month CD that has an APY of 1.3%. This rate overperforms the market average.Need more details? Credio's web page for Bell State Bank & Trust contains detailed information on their offered CD rates. Alternatively, click the button below to view the top yielding certificate of deposit offers nationwide, or to set filters to explore other offers.See Top Ten CDOffers by APY >>

 





